[1.0.4]
<ul>
<li>Variable overview now displays complex numbers with 'i'.</li>
<li>Variable add/edit dialog now supports input formulas.</li>
<li>Colored background for constants and variables.</li>
<li>Colored signalization of value correctness in add/edit variable dialog.</li>
<li>Colored signalization of name correctness in add/edit variable dialog.</li>
</ul>
