<li>Built-in "m" memory variable to store the result.</li>
<li>Changeable result/error on-the-fly mode message time limit.</li>
<li>Switchable option for selecting contents of final result after calculation, thx to Tomáš Kukučka for this.</li>
<li>Changeable font for on-thy-fly mode popup panel.</li>
